  "text": "and consider the asymptotics of n (5) (z) in the sector \u03c0/2 < arg z < 7\u03c0/12. The leading order behavior of each of the functions on the right-hand side of (4.7) is given in Proposition 1.3 (see also Figure 4 ). Inserting these asymptotics into (4.7) gives, as z \u2192 \u221e with \u03c0/2 < arg z < 7\u03c0/12, [CITATION_1] or equivalently, in the sector \u03c0/2 < arg z < 7\u03c0/12,",
